data.description: *Motivated Sellers*Welcome to River Plantation, a deed restricted community that offers an exceptional lifestyle. This stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage home was originally built as a Builder's Sales Model, ensuring premium quality. It is in impeccable condition and boasts several significant upgrades. As you enter the foyer, you will be greeted by a spacious and open living area. The grand two-step recessed ceiling, adorned with crown molding, adds a touch of elegance to the space. The open kitchen is a delightful feature, offering plenty of room for multiple cooks. The Primary bedroom is a generous size, easily accommodating even the largest furniture styles. The en-suite primary bathroom includes two separate closets, a double sink vanity, and a luxurious glass-enclosed tiled shower. One standout feature is the covered and screened lanai, which has been equipped with vinyl "Florida windows" and a ceiling fan. With the addition of an epoxy floor, this space is now a useful all-season room that requires minimal maintenance. This house is prepared for any storm with hurricane shutter protection, custom-fitted for each window and discreetly stored in the garage. the home has a power transfer switch, allowing for easy hookup of a portable generator in case of limited emergency electric power. Please note that the generator itself is not included. The garage also offers ample storage space, thanks to a full-width metal rack hanging from the ceiling. In addition to the fantastic features of this home, the River Plantation community provides its homeowners with a host of amenities. Enjoy the community pool and playground, canoe launch area for access to the Manatee River, walking nature trail, tennis courts, and basketball court. Within a short walk or drive, you'll find even more recreational options, such as Fort Hamer Park and boat ramp, which offers fishing and access to the Gulf of Mexico. It's also a great spot for dog walks. Golf enthusiasts will be pleased to know that there are courses for all skill levels located just a short drive from this wonderful home. If you're considering a home in Parrish, this one should definitely be on your list. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours.
